Language:

Java

Technologies & Frameworks:

Spring Boot: The core framework used to build the application.

Spring MVC: Handles web requests and routing.

Spring Data JPA: Used for database interactions.

Bootstrap: A CSS framework for styling the user interface.

Lombok: A library used to reduce boilerplate code in model classes.

Template Engine:

Thymeleaf: Used to generate dynamic HTML content on the server side.

Data Model:

The application uses a Task entity with an id, title, and completed status to represent to-do items.
